snippet.title: LATE NIGHT HUNGER - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
GAME PAGE➤➤https://tnp-games.itch.io/late-night-hunger

Enter a quiet town where Alex, a 9-year-old boy, lives a normal life. But when the clock strikes midnight, his house turns into a place of mystery and fear. Dark hallways, hidden rooms, and strange shadows transform his familiar home into a creepy adventure.
